ca.ualberta.cs.shinyexpensetracker.models

Class ExpenseClaimList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.shinyexpensetracker.models.Model<ExpenseClaimList>
      • ca.ualberta.cs.shinyexpensetracker.models.ExpenseClaimList

  • public class ExpenseClaimList
extends Model<ExpenseClaimList>
    Represents the collection of ExpenseClaims that exist in the application. As each part of the application should be working with the same list, ExpenseClaimList uses the Singleton pattern.
